OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777572670
OL,3,CPolice make two arrests after cyclist
OL,4,Cdies in Tynemouth collision
OL,6,FA cyclist has died after a collision
OL,7,Fwith a car in North Tyneside.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,10,Fincident on Preston Road North in
OL,11,FTynemouth at around 9pm on Wednesday
OL,12,F29 April.
OL,14,FNorthumbria Police say a black
OL,15,FVolkswagen Scirocco was travelling
OL,16,Fnorthbound when it collided with a
OL,17,Fbicycle. The rider suffered serious
OL,18,Finjuries and died in hospital a short
OL,19,Ftime later.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
