OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777572670
OL,3,CPolice make two arrests after cyclist
OL,4,Cdies in Tynemouth collision
OL,6,FTheir next of kin have been informed
OL,7,Fand are being supported by specialist
OL,8,Fofficers.
OL,10,FA 41-year-old man was arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,12,Fdangerous driving, while a 30-year-old
OL,13,Fman was arrested on suspicion of
OL,14,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,15,Fdriving. They remain in custody.
OL,17,FA section of the road was closed
OL,18,Ffollowing the collision and has since
OL,19,Fbeen reopened.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
