CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1777572670
OL,3,CPolice make two arrests after cyclist
OL,4,Cdies in Tynemouth collision
OL,6,FOfficers from the Force's Serious
OL,7,FCollision Investigation Unit have
OL,8,Flaunched an investigation and are
OL,9,Fappealing for witnesses. They are
OL,10,Fespecially keen to hear from anyone
OL,11,Fwho was in the area at the time and
OL,12,Fmay have CCTV or dashcam footage.
OL,14,FSergeant Dave Roberts said: "This is
OL,15,Fan incredibly tragic incident in which
OL,16,Fsomeone has sadly lost their life.
OL,18,F"Our thoughts remain firmly with their
OL,19,Floved ones, and we will continue to
OL,20,Foffer them any support they may need.
OL,26,@vD@]OUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
