OL,3,CPolice make two arrests after cyclist
OL,4,Cdies in Tynemouth collision
OL,6,F"Our investigation is very much
OL,7,Funderway and now, we're appealing for
OL,8,Fanyone who may have been in the area
OL,9,Fto get in touch.
OL,11,F"We know this can be a busy stretch of
OL,12,Froad connecting the coastline.
OL,14,F"If you were in the area or have any
OL,15,Finformation that might help with our
OL,16,Finvestigation, please get in touch."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOUxD@dO]
